@BankingSystem_Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7039

### Register
POST {{BankingSystem_Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "Test User",
  "email": "test.user@example.com",
  "password": "ChangeMe1!",
  "role": "user"
}

### Verify registration OTP
POST {{BankingSystem_Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test.user@example.com",
  "otp": "123456"
}

### Resend an expired registration OTP
POST {{BankingSystem_Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/resend-otp
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test.user@example.com"
}

### Login
POST {{BankingSystem_Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test.user@example.com",
  "password": "ChangeMe1!",
  "role": "user"
}

### Rotate access and refresh tokens (uses refreshToken cookie)
POST {{BankingSystem_Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/refresh-token

### Logout (uses authentication cookies)
POST {{BankingSystem_Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/logout
